    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if the veto is just this tool for dominance, does that mean the whole idea of international law is kind of a joke? like, if the most powerful countries can just ignore it whenever they want, is there even any real difference between the UN's system and just a world where everyone does whatever they want without any rules?",
